<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a8ee420-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8712"><num value="8712">§ 8712.</num><heading> Effect on other laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter shall not affect or preempt any other Federal or State law authorizing research, education, and promotion relating to concrete masonry products.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a8ee421-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/254/dE/s1313">Pub. L. 115–254, div. E, § 1313</ref>, <date date="2018-10-05">Oct. 5, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/3483">132 Stat. 3483</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
